  "content": "As a recovering underwriter, I still remember the \"good old days\" which mostly involved drowning in 30-page PDFs, cross-referencing messy SOVs, and manually hunting for NAICS codes just to see if a risk was even worth my time.\n\nFor years, we have talked about \"automation,\" but it usually just meant a slightly faster way to move data from one spreadsheet to another. Today, I am sharing an article on how we are finally moving past traditional underwriting into the era of Agentic Underwriting. How a modern \"Spine\" of infrastructure is replacing the manual grind with something much more powerful.\n\nUnderwriting shouldn't be about data entry; it should be about high-level decisioning. We are finally building the infrastructure that lets underwriters get back to the art of the deal. Check out the full article below to see how the maturity model is shifting.\n\n#Underwriting #Insurtech #AI #CommercialInsurance #AgenticAI #Bold Penguin #BindisLife #BeBold",
